  </head>

  <body role="document">

    <!-- Fixed navbar -->
    <div class="navbar navbar-default" role="navigation"><!-- navbar-fixed-top-->
      <div class="container">
        <div class="navbar-header">
          <button type="button" class="navbar-toggle" data-toggle="collapse" data-target=".navbar-collapse">
            <span class="sr-only">Toggle navigation</span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
            <span class="icon-bar"></span>
          </button>
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="<%= link %>">Daniel Morales</a>
        </div>
        <div class="collapse navbar-collapse">
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav">
            <li class="<%= current? %>"><a href="<%= link %>">Inicio</a></li>
            <li class="<%= current?('acerca.html') %>"><a href="<%= link 'acerca.html' %>">Acerca</a></li>
            <li class="<%= current?('contactar.html') %>"><a href="<%= link 'contactar.html' %>">Contactar</a></li>

            <% if logged_in? %>
            <li class="dropdown">
              <a href="#" class="dropdown-toggle" data-toggle="dropdown">Administration <b class="caret"></b></a>
              <ul class="dropdown-menu">
                <li><a href="<%= link 'admin/posts' %>">Posts</a></li>
                <li><a href="<%= link 'admin/tags' %>">Tags</a></li>
                <li><a href="<%= link 'admin/messages' %>">Messages</a></li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
          <ul class="nav navbar-nav navbar-right">
            <li><a class="rss" href="<%= link 'feed' %>" target="_blank">RSS</a></li>
            <li><a class="english" href="http://blog.daniel.com.uy/">English</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div><!--/.nav-collapse -->
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Begin page content -->
    <div class="container">
      <% if flash[:notice] %>
      <div class="alert alert-success alert-dismissable">
        <button type="button" class="close" data-dismiss="alert" aria-hidden="true">&times;</button>
        <%= flash[:notice] %>
      </div>
      <% end %>

      <div class="row">
        <div class="col-sm-8 duy-main">
          <%= yield %>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-3 col-sm-offset-1">
          <div class="sidebar-module sidebar-module-inset">
            <h4>Acerca</h4>
            <p>Dícese de un tipo que <em>programaba</em> y pasaba demasiado tiempo online; un día se decidió a finalmente escribir su blog en español. Lea el <a href="/acerca.html">Acerca</a> para saber más de esta increíble historia. <em>No</em></p>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-module sidebar-module-center">
            <script id="fedora-banner" type="text/javascript" src="http://fedoraproject.org/static/js/release-counter-ext.js?lang=es&width=200px"></script>
          </div>

          <div class="sidebar-module">
            <h4>Tags</h4>
            <ol class="list-unstyled">
            <% tags.each do |tag| %>
              <li><a href="<%= link tag.url %>"><%= tag.name %></a></li>
            <% end %>
            </ol>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div id="footer">
      <div class="container">
        <p class="text-muted">&copy; Dani Morales 2014 | Hosted on <a href="http://heroku.com/" target="_blank">Heroku</a> &amp; <a href="http://pointhq.com/" target="_blank">PointDNS</a> | Powered by <a href="http://www.sinatrarb.com/" target="_blank">Sinatra</a> | <a href="https://github.com/danielm/sinatra-blog" target="_blank">View Source</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>

